726999f-b.text:
Jamaica Ave., at the S.W. corner of 78th Street (formerly Snedeker Ave.), showing the Thos. Snedeker house of 1860. Other owners were C. Vanderveer, 1873; and C.B. Vanderveer in 1891.  It was demolished in 1924.

View 1: 1922.
View 2: 1923

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
